17. Seal Sentence

NATT-OS is not a software-only agent framework.

NATT-OS is an identity-bound operating architecture with a Sovereign Edge Hardware Field, where physical signals must pass intake, acceptance, first-signal evidence, route verification, SiraSign boundary, and audit before becoming runtime claims.
